categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This female quad-horned Jedi served the Jedi Order during the Clone Wars. In 21 BBY, she was walking within the Temple district of the Jedi Temple on the planet Coruscant. The Jedi had blonde hair, four arms and wore a robe.

The Jedi first appeared as a background character in Jedi: Yoda, a Dark Horse comic drawn by HOON and released on July 21, 2004. Concept art of the Jedi released on HOON's website depicted her with red eyes, grey skin and two green lightsabers.
